	* ext/oci8/apiwrap.yml, ext/oci8/stmt.c: call OCIStmtPrepare2()
	    without GVL to prevent OCI8#parse from blocking ruby itself
	    while the connection is used by another thread even though
	    non-blocking mode is set.

