	* VERSION: update to 2.1.0.
	* ext/oci8/error.c, ext/oci8/oci8.c, ext/oci8/oci8.h, ext/oci8/ocidatetime.c,
	  ext/oci8/ocinumber.c, ext/oci8/stmt.c: suppress gcc-4.6 warnings.

