	* lib/dbd/OCI8.rb: add code for ruby-dbi 0.4 type conversion.
	* test/test_dbi.rb: suppress deprecated warnings while running
	    test_bind_dbi_data_type.
	* test/test_dbi_clob.rb: fix a problem when running this
	    file directly.

