	  ext/oci8/oci8.c, ext/oci8/ocinumber.c, ext/oci8/rowid.c,
	  ext/oci8/stmt.c, ext/oci8/tdo.c: use TO_ORATEXT, TO_CHARPTR and
	    RSTRING_ORATEXT macros to suppress 'differ in signedness'
	    warinings.

